e width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSlwuLjzb15A/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSlwuLjzb15A/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这些数据显示，随着能源成本飙升，战争最终对美国经济造成了全面打击——随着霍尔木兹海峡关闭，而特朗普政府仍在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/CjYMqHfjYpEjGomD02g7hGQZyGZfV4pkK8VeHuFZhI51th-HhC8gj3sRJUmbMxmUQ8Fpuu-rXsAU3XNJx5_qmwJYBs2QWkMF-QnQheq1VXkIQFb31b3GlNDImZemMxKiL07zv7qMZ1iijgIPufq0It_foI9q-MvoSM62D9AGTx7_YlS1qtWNTqetRnjnSH4VSvElGI5P_woGo0XVeqh1gWz0uP8birv-kVhsE1yJePgdFUDqMTWzvR-CmGJEVR9p5MAelCNeVOauQ9lXXMuBcJnnjp0eBq2R__-DvkeRVxSsJbiLkhituJg0c35_iPm139tyVDDPpbGWrUfKSjlRNlrk8Dbzki6d9NhZ2zxh450Femkdr-mh_pqM-_ZmNm3DBhi3RBKBHRurRmGjco_CU-vRB7kfdcohzWuJ95sULmCPiH5RvTP11E-OZFCWYHpnycNSRNZo17NcMeuVSR777q_w6N7czp4-a5hugm9DIHX9EhPzUJbYxcNCxGdIfDC8t1blw9l5hOw5o5BhHP-TMRqSSte1/Dzh_3P4IYj7wFj9F9VZLUZzTenoencob/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普再次发出破坏威胁，议员质疑伊朗战争成本"&gt;努力寻找摆脱冲突的办法，&lt;/a&gt;这种情况可能会持续下去。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;政府数据显示，过去两个月天然气价格上涨了近 28%。杂货价格、租金和机票价格也较一个月前大幅上涨。持续上涨，尤其是必需品成本的上涨，可能会导致消费者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/bWgpWGNuwQMqjwnqK81cGu13Yx9YgNlKrUWSvRmY5A24oIzxIPwX_Cc79WiWBXBVO_xP5jGVlnJ1Kz7SFTvKxQsvUSZfoolIYtnlt8pBBJB0mH2FWVAsC0YvbgbS8lpKQPu_915m1sGGGqZV14P5fcZMOqXuqobD5KxzqvophXGzmDXRs9S3ubzP--wKJAlDT0yMLGL7QnhBBf7Hd-XN2CWQMnaHnOLNWx938-y3absv8i_pg16_sBwanqgWbzmlqdMqKVp40MIwGQ3phI3fs18XqvdzvP3uIPldPdb9NVAajQi4WFeWUyuoVO17T8fITfhqRF-i0COmJ-xrYcusPndXa7rjkX_riQiOuhr_kAD