.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;由于包括他自己的内政大臣在内的数十名议会议员分裂，英国首相面临着是否辞职的决定。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;伊朗战争对印度造成的损害越来越大。&lt;/strong&gt;总理纳伦德拉·莫迪呼吁&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/kSa6XocyYs5wVPfa_NlnFKj1B6Eh_5H9Az4WAmD9_sQYfNysogl7FjoKuYxxFCnbQJxXpuV5mZ1LbZCWUoxRgjy30t4zBw4Bpx5Y0HVGww9vnxhAKEnfrxYaCaa_fLw-fIWUfOt9pW-ozj9GrRU8mrC269Q4tcsj2fx9jqzsdQufQoU6jWug-OdD47CoEQxgKFfP7miY82N4Cmqm68QvJZYnHNd7tx98_ZMzDxj83CAS0PQhlbrb0fKr6l8b6cEq9DpsyCsmjVY4-h-jd1_FoMEZT7JscMg7MOEjbJvOl19UYc6dEHvKc5gQGI66lKoeYFmfaztCFOOcL8vLxP0MzlCqNedhhdJp-MVpgggUhHldzvGkkoIK5oBXhYxwRFRY3yVPu2bsImuVskPJ1haMOpSeZOmZd74uOWATQYwHiEh6S0gz4YEmCDPbg7mZK9vdgsDVMtthlLZv-xCoV7-dZ1jSbngBEm8qLDaii163i4HDnx9DCeDkqRvCdUe3m4bI0GEu0fZ0nO3BoRD2slaxutaLTg/ManpawLHM4EIhXb-6sG7poqA_9REe3Ni/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="莫迪要求印度人停止购买黄金，打击珠宝股"&gt;印度人至少在一年内避免购买黄金，&lt;/a&gt;以保存外汇储备，这对于一个黄金在储蓄、婚礼和宗教节日中发挥着至关重要作用的国家来说，这是一个令人惊讶的呼吁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;就在这一非正统要求提出的一天前，他呼吁公民&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/c3YxDIMhiwDNA0vt8EysjwsZlzkfEUTZ7WU9ffq95nTpK4lp735npiWU-JL4IU8lN6oqkBLMbq1R-n1IzPdhkgBzxgnVoy6e-Ekmr-uyphP6ws5B4mRet3eXa7pagr6GvCEJKnFHbyrK70SEkXFye2gH-PNV1yz2VBaVkvUNOjrWqYKFUshCCK-3pF3G3Hrwk78LLizeQo612P5Lj0UCuvf_q91jIYeubJJFH8K43vfrKo9OgphjtRyHJO1xg4fQ7hdaoAoOvmyaBs3IG0RB4-lluugsJVal4pTr-51mLTKghZK7hsZZVsCvJpC0RIHCDeigmSPHGGPzD_nxaynh4uuWNGfsLoleRj9P8TDljAFFxW0U0l89YIKAfkeKL-66WZ9Mshu0WRLW595hyelpvWJdAgDWf8fjKNvrAWfJymsdP58aSszx1narMwd5CVze7TJ2Ktuz8CLU-dX5bBFX9MF